narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: I think this course is very extensive.
The Slides in the second half seemed to be a little bit all over the place. Also, the weekly reading responses should be more clearly communicated.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes, I think that it gave a reasonable overview over all potential hot-topics in labor economic. It covered everything from childhood to almost retirement. Also Joe is a very knowledgeable professor from whose expertise we can learn a lot.
